n-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2530272\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 06, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104nip1665702694524.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nip1665702694524.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nip1665702694524.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"nip1665702694524\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">If the Uniface Router fails for some reason, it is automatically restarted after 10 seconds.\n </p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nip1665702694524__li_d15854e1_d15855e1_d15856e1\">To configure Uniface Router recovery on Microsoft Windows:\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nip1665702694524__li_d15857e1_d15858e1_d15859e1\">From the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Start</span> menu, choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Program Files &gt;Administrative Tools &gt;Services</span></span>.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nip1665702694524__li_d15860e1_d15861e1_d15862e1\">Select the Uniface Router service (for example, <code class=\"ph codeph\">Uniface10 URouter</code>), right-click and choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Properties</span>.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nip1665702694524__li_d15863e1_d15864e1_d15865e1\">In the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Recovery</span> tab, set the properties as desired.\n <p class=\"p\" id=\"nip1665702694524__p_d31082e1_d31083e1_d31084e1\">By default, the properties are set as follows:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"nip1665702694524__table_d3206e1_d3207e1_d3208e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nip1665702694524__table_d3206e1_d3207e1_d3208e1__entry__1\">\n Property\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nip1665702694524__table_d3206e1_d3207e1_d3208e1__entry__2\">\n Value\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nip1665702694524__table_d3206e1_d3207e1_d3208e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">First Failure</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nip1665702694524__table_d3206e1_d3207e1_d3208e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Restart the Service</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nip1665702694524__table_d3206e1_d3207e1_d3208e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Second Failure</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nip1665702694524__table_d3206e1_d3207e1_d3208e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Restart the Service</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nip1665702694524__table_d3206e1_d3207e1_d3208e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Subsequent Failures</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nip1665702694524__table_d3206e1_d3207e1_d3208e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Take No Action</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nip1665702694524__p_d31085e1_d31086e1_d31087e1\">These settings ensure that if the Uniface Router stops again within 60 seconds, it is restarted after 30 seconds. If it crashes a second time in 60 seconds, it is not restarted.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nip1665702694524__li_d15866e1_d15867e1_d15868e1\">On Unix, if you want to change\n            the crash behavior, edit the <span class=\"ph filepath\">urouter.sh</span>.  </li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/luh1665702694600.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>urouter.sh</a><p>Unix script for starting the Uniface Router.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530272\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530272\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Configure Uniface Router Recovery Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 06, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 If the Uniface Router fails for some reason, it is automatically restarted after 10 seconds. To configure Uniface Router recovery on Microsoft Windows: From the Start menu, choose Program Files >Administrative Tools >Services . Select the Uniface Router service (for example, Uniface10 URouter ), right-click and choose Properties . In the Recovery tab, set the properties as desired. By default, the properties are set as follows: Property Value First Failure Restart the Service Second Failure Restart the Service Subsequent Failures Take No Action These settings ensure that if the Uniface Router stops again within 60 seconds, it is restarted after 30 seconds. If it crashes a second time in 60 seconds, it is not restarted. On Unix, if you want to change the crash behavior, edit the urouter.sh . Related Links urouter.sh Unix script for starting the Uniface Router. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}